They have such beautiful eyes.

653
00:31:49.770 --> 00:31:50.770
As if...

654
00:31:52.210 --> 00:31:53.210
As if they're scared.

655
00:31:54.130 --> 00:31:55.130
But they aren't.

656
00:31:56.300 --> 00:31:57.340
